&lt;p&gt;Well, this shall happen no more. I&amp;#8217;m starting a new scheme this year in which on January 1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; of each year, I donate to all the organizations that make the&amp;nbsp;cut. &lt;/p&gt;
